        • goalCaret

          int goalCaret
          The goal caret represents the position of the caret immediately before and after an edit, and it is set whenever one of the EditEvents is undone or redone. The DocumentListener part of this class is called shortly afterward, and it attempts to relocate the cursor to where it had been when the edit was made.
